column2: "For everyone, I guess this is normal, but there's so much new stuff to me."
"Like the monitors in the lobby. At first I thought the wall was moving!"
"I've lost my memory, and it's inconvenient, but normal stuff is interesting to me now."
"Of course, I'm doing my best to remember. I haven't forgotten that."
"But I think that forgetting may not be such a bad thing."
